              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2452289"/>Combat<a href="img/EpicMonsters(G-W).Umbral_Blot.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/EpicMonsters(G-W).Umbral_Blot.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></h5>
